Sharp, Hon Hai Precision Agree to Form LCD Parts Procurement Venture

-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 
2011-07-15T08:38:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/sharp-hon-hai-precision-agree-to-form-lcd-parts-procurement-venture.html
Sharp Corp. and Hon Hai Precision
Industry Co. agreed on July 2 to form a venture to procure parts
for liquid-crystal-displays. The companies will also supply LCDs
to one another, Miyuki Nakayama, a spokeswoman for Sharp, said
by telephone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariko Yasu in Tokyo at 
